             was indicted for <rs id="t17850629-49-off234" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850629-49-off234" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850629-49-off234" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850629-49-cd235" type="crimeDate">17th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-49-off234 t17850629-49-cd235"></join>, one linen handkerchief, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850629-49-victim452" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Crowther
                  <interp inst="t17850629-49-victim452" type="surname" value="Crowther"></interp>
